{"tid":598077,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔成日笑人睇content farm","createTime":"2018-03-19T08:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T13:43:52.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"64352f8052a72393e28e5e6ce99b3dac9731b612","tid":598077,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"其實google早在2011年，已經留意到content farm的問題<br />\n<br />\nGoogle的AI, algorithm亦經常更新。Google也有專人去處理呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n低質的content farm, 其實多已被google剔走，或放在lower ranking中。<br />\n<br />\n只保留高質content farm在high ranking。<br />\n<br />\n相反，連登仔，睇唔起經過google 的人工智能過濾過的content farm的文章。只會看任何人都可以post的連登、高登、discuss。"},{"pid":"61c01d3369eec552166f33c235ce97cbd35a7005","tid":598077,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mashable.com/2011/02/25/google-content-farms/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2F2011%2F02%2F25%2Fgoogle-content-farms%2F&d=oK81T%2BzW%2FRBjANvf%2FMit2cP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=3b7ad8ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mashable.com/2011/02/25/google-content-farms/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://searchengineland.com/google-forecloses-on-content-farms-with-farmer-algorithm-update-66071\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsearchengineland.com%2Fgoogle-forecloses-on-content-farms-with-farmer-algorithm-update-66071&d=oK81T%2BzW%2FRBjANvf%2FMit2cP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=59eac9b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://searchengineland.com/google-forecloses-on-content-farms-with-farmer-algorithm-update-66071</a>"},{"pid":"bc735e4f5897a8184c23d96d4e78787455e785c0","tid":598077,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"重要聲明<br />\n這篇文唔係話content farm好野<br />\n<br />\n相反，睇論文，睇書，甚至睇wiki, 都比睇content farm好得多<br />\n<br />\n只係你笑人睇content farm唔代表你聰明，因為content farm冇你想到差成咁。"},{"pid":"2df36c695f3fb7818d27c09d7e47a161a374abb2","tid":598077,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T13:43:52.000Z","msg":"content farm係差，<br />\n但冇連登你想像中咁萬惡不赦，<br />\n因為有search engine filter過，<br />\n同埋好多content farm對寫手都有返d要求。<br />\n不過content farm 料仍係差，好多係copycat，但情況唔係超級惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n真實的content farm<br />\n大部分係copycat<br />\n<br />\n在網上做完研究再copy and rephrase<br />\n<br />\ncontent farm最大壞處和衰格左破壞知識產權。<br />\n<br />\n好處係rephrase過，令讀者易明些和易d比search engine搵到。"}]}